HEADWORD: Corno Inglese
<hw>Cor"no In*gle"se</hw> <pr>(?n-gl?"z?)</pr>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Corni Inglesi</plw> <pr>(-z<?/)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[It.]</ety>
